text:
Hello everyone! I came across an odd bug, when printing HubDB's date with HubL for the last 4 days of the 2025 (28-31 December 2025) it's printing them with a 2026 year. It works just fine by applying any other dates but them, I've tested with 27th of December and 01 January 2026.

Is anybody having the same issue?

For more context, I'm looping through the dates and printing the dates in the HubDB as follows:

```{% for row in data %}
   {{row.date | format_date('d-M-YYYY')}}
{% endfor %}```
